==English [[Leet]]==

===Noun===
'''n00b'''

# (''online gaming'') A [[newbie]]; an ineffective player.  May be used attributively.
#: ''That was a total n00b move, but what do you expect from a n00b?''
# (''internet'') One who posts foolishly on an [[internet]] [[forum]]/message board
#: ''The n00b posted a very stupid reply, not realizing that he was on the first page of an 18-page topic, and was harassed for it.''
